Description: Three fragments of fine dark brown string, made of human hair and used as binding. The string consists of 3 's'-spun elements, 'z'-plied together, with an average diameter of 1.62 mm.
Bibliographic references: Adams et al 1999 / Kulubnarti III: The Cemeteries (p. 64)
